    • Method Detail

      • getServerCode

        public String getServerCode()
        Gets optional REST server error code.
        Returns:
        REST server error code or null. If not null - one of the following values:
        • NC_INVALID_ACCESS_TOKEN
        • NC_SIGNIN_FAILURE
        • NC_NOT_IMPLEMENTED
        • NC_INVALID_FIELD
        • NC_ADMIN_REQUIRED
        • NC_INVALID_OPERATION
        • NC_ERROR
        • NC_UNEXPECTED_ERROR
        See openapi/nlpcraft_swagger.yml file for details.
